# Employee Attendance & KPI Dashboard

This project is a **full-stack employee attendance tracking system** with a **Django REST API backend** and an **Angular frontend**.  
It allows HR/admins to **upload attendance data from Excel files**, compute **working hours**, and visualize **KPIs** (best employee, worst employee, weekly trends, realized/remaining hours, etc.) on a modern dashboard.

---

## 🎥 Demo Video

https://github.com/mell0wO/DataPulse/new/raw/main/demo.mp4


## 🚀 Features

- 📂 **Excel Import**: Upload `.xls` or `.xlsx` files containing attendance records.  
- ⏱ **Automatic Time Calculation**: Computes daily working hours, cumulative hours, and detects absences.  
- 📊 **Dashboard KPIs**:
  - Best & Worst Employee
  - Total & Average Hours
  - Weekly Trends (Lun → Dim)
  - Realized vs Remaining Hours
- 👩‍💼 **Employee View**: List of employees with their daily check-in/check-out and cumulative hours.  
- 🌐 **REST API** with **Django Rest Framework** for seamless frontend integration.  
- 🎨 **Angular Frontend**:
  - Modern responsive UI
  - Sidebar navigation (Accueil, Dashboard, Logout)
  - Charts (bar & donut graphs)

